headline: 2 No-Brainer Fintech Stocks to Buy With $1,000 Right Now
summary: PayPal just reported excellent numbers, but the stock is barely moving.  There is a great deal of uncertainty surrounding tariff policy, interest rates, consumer confidence, and just the economy in general.  Two that could be worth a closer look right now are fintech leaders PayPal (NASDAQ: PYPL) and SoFi Technologies (NASDAQ: SOFI).
